  "texts": [
    "To complement these findings, we collected the participants' subjective views to understand their personal experiences with the training process.",
    "These subjective experiences are crucial for interpreting the objective results, offering insights into the specific features of the ChatGPT training, which participants found beneficial.",
    "By examining these perspectives, we aim to uncover the factors contributing to their improved performance.",
    "At the end of each participant's training, we collected their subjective opinions about the learning process with ChatGPT.",
    "Our study's qualitative analysis suggests that 90% of these opinions were positive."
